Welcome to Whaling Road in North Sydney, where you'll discover a comfortable, fully furnished ground-floor apartment. This space includes one bedroom, one bathroom, and secure off-street parking. In the bedroom, there's a Queen-sized bed and a ceiling fan. The bathroom is modern and well-appointed, and the slick kitchen is fully equipped with Miele appliances. A dining area is available for enjoying your meals, and the living room features air conditioning for a comfortable environment. Entertainment options include a Smart TV, Apple TV, and a BOSE Bluetooth Speaker, all within reach. Stay connected with high-speed Wi-Fi during your visit. There's an undercover patio with a table and chairs, along with a fan for those warm days. You'll also find a charming courtyard where you can enjoy the fresh air.

Located on the residential side of North Sydney, you'll have easy access to the CBD, major supermarkets, train stations, bus stops, North Sydney Wharf, and the iconic Sydney Harbour Bridge. Dining options, cafes, and shops are all just a short walk away. Explore the charming neighbourhood of Kirribilli, known for its historic homes, waterfront walks, and a variety of dining options. This area is also home to notable landmarks like Admiralty House and Kirribilli House. For those who appreciate outdoor activities, several nearby parks, such as Milsons Park and St Leonards Park, offer scenic green spaces. Don't miss the Kirribilli Markets, known for its artisan fashions, jewellery, delicious foods, and unique gifts. Nearby, you'll find exclusive clubs like the Royal Sydney Yacht Squadron and Kirribilli RSL. Golf enthusiasts can enjoy a round at the Cammeray Public Golf Club, and if you're looking for a fresh perspective on the city, consider the Sydney Kayak Experience. You can paddle past iconic landmarks like the Opera House, Harbour Bridge, and Luna Park while enjoying stunning views of the sunrise, sunset, or city lights. To cool off, take a refreshing dip at Marrinawi Cove, a lovely spot near Barangaroo Reserve on the opposite side of the bridge.

Experience the vibrant city life of North Sydney and the tranquillity of its natural beauty during your stay at Whaling Road.
